{"type":"message","id":"6fe5aa4b","parentId":"73598ebb","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:52:57.391Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-03-04 09:52 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你是 spec-code-team 的测试工程师探雷。\n\n**任务：** 为 video-gen-pro 生成测试计划文档\n\n**工作区：** F:\\2025ideazdjx\\openClaw-project\\feature\\video-gen-pro\\\n\n**参考已完成的文档：**\n- Phase 1: 需求规格 (requirements-spec.md)\n- Phase 2: 技术设计 (technical-design.md) - 含 CLIP 实现细节\n- Phase 3: 数据契约 (data-contract.md)\n\n**生成测试计划文档，包含以下核心章节：**\n\n1. **单元测试** - ProjectManager, FlowController, ProtagonistDB, ClipValidator\n2. **集成测试** - 端到端工作流、断点恢复、并行执行\n3. **CLIP 专项测试** - 相似度阈值 0.85 校准、多图平均、缓存测试\n4. **失败恢复测试** - API 超时重试、降级方案、检查点恢复\n5. **性能基准** - 端到端<10 分钟、并发≥2、CLIP 推理性能\n6. **验收标准** - 功能/质量/性能三类验收\n\n**输出文档：** `video-gen-pro-test-plan.md`\n\n请生成完整文档并保存到工作区。"}],"timestamp":1772589177386}}
