{"type":"message","id":"197a1108","parentId":"fd20d11f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:54:57.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经阅读了三份参考文档：\n1. requirements-spec.md - 需求规格文档\n2. technical-design.md - 技术设计文档（含 CLIP 实现细节）\n3. data-contract.md - 数据契约文档\n\n现在我需要基于这些文档生成测试计划文档。测试计划应包含以下核心章节：\n\n1. 单元测试 - ProjectManager, FlowController, ProtagonistDB, ClipValidator\n2. 集成测试 - 端到端工作流、断点恢复、并行执行\n3. CLIP 专项测试 - 相似度阈值 0.85 校准、多图平均、缓存测试\n4. 失败恢复测试 - API 超时重试、降级方案、检查点恢复\n5. 性能基准 - 端到端<10 分钟、并发≥2、CLIP 推理性能\n6. 验收标准 - 功能/质量/性能三类验收\n\n我需要生成一份详细的测试计划文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我来生成完整的测试计划文档。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1772589199087,"errorMessage":"Request was aborted"}}
